---
// Modern Features Section with Pines-UI design and Alpine.js
---
<section id="features" class="py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50" x-data="{ isVisible: false }" x-intersect="isVisible = true">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-3 sm:px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16" x-show="isVisible" x-transition.duration.800ms>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        <span>المميزات</span>
        <span class="text-primary">الرئيسية</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 sm:w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary mx-auto mb-4 scroll-reveal"></div>
      <p class="text-black mt-4 sm:mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg scroll-reveal">
        نقدم مجموعة من المميزات المصممة خصيصًا لتلبية احتياجات أصحاب المتاجر والمطاعم وموردي الأغذية، مع تسهيل تجربة الشراء للمشترين الأفراد. </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100" x-show="isVisible" x-transition.delay.200ms x-data="{ hovered: false }" @mouseenter="hovered = true" @mouseleave="hovered = false">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 transition-transform duration-300" :class="{ 'rotate-12 scale-110': hovered }">
          <i class="ri-shopping-cart-line text-white text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">تجربة تسوق سهلة</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          واجهة سهلة الاستخدام تمكنك من طلب المنتجات بضغطة زر، مع تتبع فوري لطلباتك.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 flex items-center text-primary font-medium cursor-pointer hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">اعرف المزيد</span>
          <i class="ri-arrow-left-line mr-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100" x-show="isVisible" x-transition.delay.400ms x-data="{ hovered: false }" @mouseenter="hovered = true" @mouseleave="hovered = false">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 bg-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 transition-transform duration-300" :class="{ 'rotate-12 scale-110': hovered }">
          <i class="ri-price-tag-3-line text-white text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">أسعار جملة للجميع</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          استفد من أسعار الجملة على جميع المنتجات، سواء كنت تشتري لنفسك أو لعملك.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 flex items-center text-primary font-medium cursor-pointer hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">اعرف المزيد</span>
          <i class="ri-arrow-left-line mr-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100" x-show="isVisible" x-transition.delay.600ms x-data="{ hovered: false }" @mouseenter="hovered = true" @mouseleave="hovered = false">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 bg-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 transition-transform duration-300" :class="{ 'rotate-12 scale-110': hovered }">
          <i class="ri-store-2-line text-white text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">تنوع المنتجات</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          اختر من بين آلاف المنتجات من مختلف الموردين الموثوقين، مع تقييمات من عملاء سابقين.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 flex items-center text-primary font-medium cursor-pointer hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">اعرف المزيد</span>
          <i class="ri-arrow-left-line mr-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100" x-show="isVisible" x-transition.delay.800ms x-data="{ hovered: false }" @mouseenter="hovered = true" @mouseleave="hovered = false">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 bg-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6 transition-transform duration-300" :class="{ 'rotate-12 scale-110': hovered }">
          <i class="ri-customer-service-2-line text-white text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">دعم فني متكامل</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          فريق دعم متخصص جاهز لمساعدتك في أي وقت، لضمان تجربة تسوق سلسة ومريحة.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 flex items-center text-primary font-medium cursor-pointer hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">اعرف المزيد</span>
          <i class="ri-arrow-left-line mr-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>